  "title": "ACTA/ACLP First Aid / BCLS+AED Instructor (Freelance/Contract) (Paramedics, EMTs, and Nurses Welcome to Apply!)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for passionate and dedicated freelance/contract instructors to conduct First Aid, CPR+AED, and BCLS+AED courses in accordance with the latest guidelines set by the Singapore Resuscitation and First Aid Council (SRFAC).</p>\n<h3>Description</h3>\n<p>As an instructor, you will:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver engaging and accurate training sessions to participants from various backgrounds.</li>\n  <li>Communicate effectively to ensure participants understand key lifesaving skills and concepts.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and upkeep training equipment and materials.</li>\n  <li>Support administrative tasks such as attendance tracking, assessment documentation, and feedback collection.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Requirements (Must-Have)</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to work collaboratively as part of a team</li>\n  <li>Commitment to upholding training standards and SRFAC guidelines</li>\n  <li>BCLS+AED Instructor Certification (Training can be provided by SERA for individuals with a healthcare background)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Requirements (Good-to-Have)</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Paramedic, EMT, or Nursing background</li>\n  <li>First Aid Instructor Certification</li>\n  <li>Code of Ethics</li>\n  <li>WSQ Advanced Certificate in Learning and Performance /  Advanced Certificate in Training and Assessment (ACTA/ACLP)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The courses you may be assigned to teach will depend on the qualifications and certifications you hold.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. Thank you! </p>\n<p><br></p>",
